dct_description_sm: Inset: The Bermuda Islands. Relief indicated by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. In upper margin: 44. "Entered according to Act of Congress in the Year 1864 by A.J. Johnson ... " Probably issued in: Johnson's new illustrated (steel plate) family atlas ... New York : Johnson and Ward, 1864.
